# Authentication for this course
#
# By default this course uses your Claude Pro/Max SUBSCRIPTION -- no API key needed.
# Just install the Claude Code CLI and run `claude` once to log in:
#   curl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash   # then: claude
#
# OPTIONAL: to use per-token API billing instead of your subscription, uncomment
# the line below and paste a key from https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# IMPORTANT: if ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set, it OVERRIDES your subscription.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
